<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. إِنَّ الْمُغِيثَ اللهُ لِلإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَا قَوْمُ فَأدْعُو اللهَ لا تَدْعُوا الْوَرَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنْتُمْ وَهُمْ بِالْفَقْرِ مَوْسُومَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا بَالُكُمْ لَمْ تُخْلِصُوا تَوْحِيدَكُمْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَوْحِيدُكُمْ وَالشِّرْكُ مُقْتَرَنَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هَا أَنْتُمُوا أَشْبَهْتُمُوا مَنْ قَبْلَكُمْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِي شِرْكِهِمْ بِعِبَادَةِ الدَّيَّانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِنْ كَانَ هَذَا الْفِعْلُ لا يُسْمَوْنَهُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بِعِبَادَةِ فَهِيَ اسْمُهُ الْقُرْآنِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مَعْنَى الْعِبَادَةِ ثَابِتٌ مُتَحَقَّقٌ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فِي فِعْلِكُمْ شَرْعًا وَعُرْفِ لِسَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِنَّ الدُّعَاءَ عِبَادَةٌ بَلْ مُخُّهَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَدْ قَالَ ذَا مَنْ جَاءَ بِالْفُرْقَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَإِذَا زَعَمْتُمْ أَنَّهُمْ شُفَعَاؤُكُمْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تَتَوَسَّلُونَ بِهِمْ إِلَى الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَالْجَاهِلِيَّةُ كَانَ هَذَا زَعْمُهُمْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَيْضًا وَقَدْ نُسِبُوا إِلَى الْكُفْرَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مَا كَانَ أَهْلُ الشِّرْكِ يَعْتَقِدُونَهُمْ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>خَلَقُوا هُمُوا يَا جَاهِلَ الْقُرْآنِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَاللهُ مَا شَرَعَ التَّوَسَّلَ لِلْوَرَى<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِلا بِطَاعَتِهِ مَعَ الإِيمَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>